# Visual Testing Guide

## Step-by-Step Visual Guide

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Initial Setup (Terminal)

**What you type:**
```bash
npx create-next-app@latest lazorkit-starter --typescript --tailwind --app
cd lazorkit-starter
npm install @lazorkit/wallet @solana/web3.js @solana/spl-token buffer
```

**What you should see:**
```
âœ” Creating project in lazorkit-starter
âœ” Installing dependencies...
âœ” Initialized git repository

added 342 packages in 45s
```

**âœ… Success indicators:**
- No error messages
- "added XXX packages" message appears
- New folder `lazorkit-starter` created

---

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Starting Development Server

**What you type:**
```bash
npm run dev
```

**What you should see:**
```
  â–² Next.js 15.1.3
  - Local:        http://localhost:3000
  - Network:      http://192.168.1.x:3000

 âœ“ Starting...
 âœ“ Ready in 2.5s
```

**âœ… Success indicators:**
- "Ready in X.Xs" message
- No compilation errors
- Port 3000 is listening

**âŒ Common errors:**
```
Error: listen EADDRINUSE: address already in use :::3000
```
**Fix:** Another app is using port 3000. Run `npm run dev -- -p 3001` instead

